</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut the 3 cable ties. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_74B6A4D2B2584F2289F17E2100032268" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A14EC4AA-E9E8-41CC-BB97-3186018CCE2A-low.png" id="IMAGE_FB756E144D6343D49D5E238CA3CC2BEB" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A14EC4AA-E9E8-41CC-BB97-3186018CCE2A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
