</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Loosen the 2 screws. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_9FB0C7F095B548A68A0EF5DAA64F9B1A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B185BB3F-ECB8-406D-8A59-AD7D65122FCE-low.png" id="IMAGE_A8C4A44D3FF041C4B04E35475700743A" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B185BB3F-ECB8-406D-8A59-AD7D65122FCE-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_3A11E562E7EE4DB988B35F61658AF545" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D96AB9F7-4C4E-4CF3-B86E-D44082BF36D5-low.png" id="IMAGE_F6DB51FB08604BBB89B2C8FB20029411" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D96AB9F7-4C4E-4CF3-B86E-D44082BF36D5-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Loosen the 2 screws of the bracket. 
